<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Controller_Response_Abstract has behaviour dealing with HTTP (headers, response codes).</p>

<p>This belongs in Zend_Controller_Response_Http.</p>

<p>Currently, Zend_Controller_Response_Cli is exposed to a HTTP implementation, while Zend_Controller_Response_Http is empty.</p>

